                  </origin>
                  <provenance><locus target="#1r #4r" facs="001 004">Fols. 1r, 4r</locus>The manuscript is from Maqdala. On 1r is the number 813; and at the top of 4r is written: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድጓ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም</foreign></provenance>
